{"tid":2182630,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★八達通將可在中國大陸使用   總裁：冀一卡通行中國交通工具","createTime":"2020-08-31T12:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T12:55:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"89ce1bdb9c26d379f8ea0cece72d875166e5f85e","tid":2182630,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T12:21:01.000Z","msg":"八達通在本年正式加入 Apple Pay 服務後，其擴展電子支付的野心更大。八達通總裁最近表示，目前正計劃向非接觸式卡方向發展，短期目標是港人可利用<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>八達通在中國大陸支付車費</strong></span>，增加跨境連接。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n現年 66 歲的八達通控股公司總裁張耀堂於今日（31 日）卸任，上周接受傳媒採訪時表示，八達通未來有五大目標，一是繼 Samsung 及 iPhone 後，期望將來所有手機都能開通八達通功能；二是簽定更多合作商戶，以搶佔現時佔比仍達 30% 的現金支付市場；三是希望發展更多商用版八達通 App 服務，拓展如中小型零售商戶和的士司機等客戶；四是繼續多做線上支付服務；至於<span class=\"xx-large\">第五個目標</span>，就是擴張業務版圖，向中國以及世界出發，讓港人一張<span class=\"xx-large\">八達通卡在手，便可通行全中國以至全世界的公共交通</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/08/31/octopus-card-china/life-tech/epayment/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F08%2F31%2Foctopus-card-china%2Flife-tech%2Fepayment%2F&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr01T2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=900499aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/08/31/octopus-card-china/life-tech/epayment/</a>"},{"pid":"a34db3d7ca4faced539d8aedcc15ade0f9876d1a","tid":2182630,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T12:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071a7a3b4e0fd2fcb835f191c81b69d87d0abb69","tid":2182630,"uid":153811,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20